"""
=============================================================================
COMIC BOOK GENERATOR — "Sequential Art Edition"
=============================================================================
A full-pipeline comic book synthesizer that builds on the novel generator's
infrastructure (character graph EI, image generation, story idea synthesis)
but produces page-paneled comics with dialogue bubbles, captions, SFX, and
publication-ready PDF + DOCX outputs.

ARCHITECTURE:
    Phase 1 — Story synthesis (reuses novel generator's story idea + characters)
    Phase 2 — Comic script (page-by-page panel breakdown with dialogue)
    Phase 3 — Page layout planning (variable layouts per page)
    Phase 4 — Visual DNA (Story/Page/Panel three-tier)
    Phase 5 — Panel image generation (4 variants per panel)
    Phase 6 — Text overlay (PIL speech bubbles, captions, SFX)
    Phase 7 — Page composition (PIL stitches panels into pages)
    Phase 8 — Output (PDF + DOCX + CBZ + manifest for re-editing)

USAGE:
    from comic_book_generator import synthesize_comic_book
    synthesize_comic_book(
        story_idea_str="Your story concept...",
        target_pages=24,
        creative_seeds={...},
    )

EDIT WORKFLOW:
    1. Run generator once → produces docx + pdf + manifest
    2. Open docx in Word, review pages
    3. To swap an image: edit manifest.json to change variant number (e.g. 1→3)
    4. Re-run rebuild_from_manifest() to regenerate pages with new selections
    5. Re-run build_outputs() to regenerate pdf/docx with updates

=============================================================================
"""

