# =============================================================================
# SPIRITUAL AURA & EMOTIONAL COLOUR COMPOSITION SYSTEM
# =============================================================================
# Chakra-inspired colour palette mapped to emotional/spiritual states.
# These auras apply SELECTIVELY — only when a panel is flagged with
# `spiritual_intensity` (a new optional LLM field, see script generation
# instructions). Regular emotional scenes do NOT get auras; only panels
# where the story is making an explicit spiritual/transcendent statement.
#
# Colour philosophy (mirroring chakra tradition but not rigidly):
#   LOVE / COMPASSION      → warm golden-amber, rose-gold, heart-green
#   ANGER / PASSION        → blood-crimson, fire-orange outer corona
#   SADNESS / ISOLATION    → deep indigo, cool violet, midnight blue
#   COSMIC CONNECTION      → royal purple, ultraviolet crown, starfield
